{Name}{}{Drunkard}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see a drunkard.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see some ragged drunkard staggering from side to side. His face is swollen, his nose looks like a plum. He smells so bad even brahmin wouldn't stand the stench. He is mumbling something and singing loudly from time to time...}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see a drunkard. He is very dirty, seems he fell into to some puddle, but he doesn't appear to be upset after all.}
{Speech 1}{}{Initial preferences}
{Speech 1 Answer 7}{}{-}
{Speech 1 Answer 8}{}{-}
{Speech 2}{}{Do you have a cure for my wounded... hiccup... soul?}
