{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{Here, have a beer. I am stocked up with booze today. [You give him a bottle of beer]}
{Speech 2 Answer 4*}{}{Have some vodka! [You give him a bottle of vodka]}
{Speech 2 Answer 6}{}{Go away, dickhead!@@Move along, drunkard!@@Go annoy somebody else.}
