{Speech 6}{}{Can somebody help me?@@Go away!@@Leave me alone.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Bye. [Leave]}
{Speech 7}{}{Wow, your face is completely pale.@@Don't tell them, we know that there's nothing there.@@Ohhhh...@@Can you see me?@@Be vewy vewy quieeet, pleaaaase.. I'm hunting wabbits!@@How'd you get there?@@Shhh! I am hiding, so nobody can find me...@@I can run faster than a wolf!@@I'm feeling so fine!@@This is in my blood...@@Right there, baby.@@Wow, can you feel the force?@@Wow, you're glowing...@@I love you, @sex@|man|girl|!@@What a wonderful life! What about yours?@@Little ones are flying in the night.@@Say hello to my little friend.@@I want to sleep, buddy...@@Did you see my dog?@@Shhh, they're right behind you...@@Ooh, my head.@@So much pain..@@I'm shaking. Can't stop shaking..@@Ooh, I need some more.@@I can't wait! I need more! Right now!@@Taking away my shit?@@Hey, did you hear about anything called G.E.C.K.? I am looking for it...}
